<li><i><a href="/wiki/Deathworld" title="Deathworld">Deathworld</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Harry_Harrison" title="Harry Harrison">Harry Harrison</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Venus_Plus_X" title="Venus Plus X">Venus Plus X</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Theodore_Sturgeon" title="Theodore Sturgeon">Theodore Sturgeon</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="vertical-align:top;">
<th>1960</th>
<td><i><a href="/wiki/Starship_Troopers" title="Starship Troopers">Starship Troopers</a></i><br />
by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a></td>
<td>
<ul>
<li>2 <i><a href="/wiki/Dorsai!" title="Dorsai!">Dorsai!</a></i> (alternate title: <i>The Genetic General</i>) by <a href="/wiki/Gordon_R._Dickson" title="Gordon R. Dickson">Gordon R. Dickson</a></li>
<li><i>The Pirates of Ersatz</i> (book title: <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Pirates_of_Zan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Pirates of Zan (page does not exist)">The Pirates of Zan</a></i>) by <a href="/wiki/Murray_Leinster" title="Murray Leinster">Murray Leinster</a></li>
<li><i>That Sweet Little Old Lady</i> (book title: <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Brain_Twister&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Brain Twister (page does not exist)">Brain Twister</a></i>) by <a href="/wiki/Mark_Phillips_(author)" title="Mark Phillips (author)">Mark Phillips</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Sirens_of_Titan" title="The Sirens of Titan">The Sirens of Titan</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Kurt_Vonnegut,_Jr." title="Kurt Vonnegut, Jr." class="mw-redirect">Kurt Vonnegut, Jr.</a></li>
