<li><i><a href="/wiki/Who%3F_(novel)" title="Who? (novel)">Who?</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Algis_Budrys" title="Algis Budrys">Algis Budrys</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Have_Space_Suit_%E2%80%94_Will_Travel" title="Have Space Suit — Will Travel" class="mw-redirect">Have Space Suit — Will Travel</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a></li>
<li><i>Time Killer</i> (book title (expanded): <i><a href="/wiki/Immortality,_Inc." title="Immortality, Inc.">Immortality, Inc.</a></i>) by <a href="/wiki/Robert_Sheckley" title="Robert Sheckley">Robert Sheckley</a></li>
