<td class="navbox-group" style=";background: #EEDD82;"><a href="/wiki/Hugo_Award_for_Best_Novel#Retro_Hugos" title="Hugo Award for Best Novel">Retro Hugos</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Foundation_and_Empire" title="Foundation and Empire">The Mule</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Isaac_Asimov" title="Isaac Asimov">Isaac Asimov</a> (1946)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Farmer_in_the_Sky" title="Farmer in the Sky">Farmer in the Sky</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1951)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Fahrenheit_451" title="Fahrenheit 451">Fahrenheit 451</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Ray_Bradbury" title="Ray Bradbury">Ray Bradbury</a> (1954)</span></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";background: #EEDD82;">1953–1960</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Demolished_Man" title="The Demolished Man">The Demolished Man</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Alfred_Bester" title="Alfred Bester">Alfred Bester</a> (1953)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/They%27d_Rather_Be_Right" title="They'd Rather Be Right">They'd Rather Be Right</a></i> (aka: The Forever Machine) by <a href="/wiki/Mark_Clifton" title="Mark Clifton">Mark Clifton</a> and <a href="/wiki/Frank_Riley_(Author)" title="Frank Riley (Author)" class="mw-redirect">Frank Riley</a> (1955)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Double_Star" title="Double Star">Double Star</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1956)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Big_Time" title="The Big Time">The Big Time</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Fritz_Leiber" title="Fritz Leiber">Fritz Leiber</a> (1958)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/A_Case_of_Conscience" title="A Case of Conscience">A Case of Conscience</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/James_Blish" title="James Blish">James Blish</a> (1959)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Starship_Troopers" title="Starship Troopers">Starship Troopers</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1960)</span></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";background: #EEDD82;">1961–1970</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/A_Canticle_for_Leibowitz" title="A Canticle for Leibowitz">A Canticle for Leibowitz</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Walter_M._Miller,_Jr." title="Walter M. Miller, Jr.">Walter M. Miller, Jr.</a> (1961)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Stranger_in_a_Strange_Land" title="Stranger in a Strange Land">Stranger in a Strange Land</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1962)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Man_in_the_High_Castle" title="The Man in the High Castle">The Man in the High Castle</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Philip_K._Dick" title="Philip K. Dick">Philip K. Dick</a> (1963)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Way_Station_(novel)" title="Way Station (novel)">Here Gather the Stars</a></i> (aka: <i>Way Station</i>) by <a href="/wiki/Clifford_D._Simak" title="Clifford D. Simak">Clifford D. Simak</a> (1964)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Wanderer_(Fritz_Leiber_novel)" title="The Wanderer (Fritz Leiber novel)">The Wanderer</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Fritz_Leiber" title="Fritz Leiber">Fritz Leiber</a> (1965)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Dune_(novel)" title="Dune (novel)">Dune</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Frank_Herbert" title="Frank Herbert">Frank Herbert</a> and <i><a href="/wiki/...And_Call_Me_Conrad" title="...And Call Me Conrad" class="mw-redirect">...And Call Me Conrad</a></i> (aka: <i>This Immortal</i>) by <a href="/wiki/Roger_Zelazny" title="Roger Zelazny">Roger Zelazny</a> (1966)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Moon_Is_a_Harsh_Mistress" title="The Moon Is a Harsh Mistress">The Moon Is a Harsh Mistress</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_A._Heinlein" title="Robert A. Heinlein">Robert A. Heinlein</a> (1967)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Lord_of_Light" title="Lord of Light">Lord of Light</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Roger_Zelazny" title="Roger Zelazny">Roger Zelazny</a> (1968)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Stand_on_Zanzibar" title="Stand on Zanzibar">Stand on Zanzibar</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/John_Brunner_(novelist)" title="John Brunner (novelist)">John Brunner</a> (1969)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Left_Hand_of_Darkness" title="The Left Hand of Darkness">The Left Hand of Darkness</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Ursula_K._Le_Guin" title="Ursula K. Le Guin">Ursula K. Le Guin</a> (1970)</span></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
