<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Harry_Potter_and_the_Goblet_of_Fire" title="Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire">Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/J.K._Rowling" title="J.K. Rowling" class="mw-redirect">J.K. Rowling</a> (2001)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/American_Gods" title="American Gods">American Gods</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Neil_Gaiman" title="Neil Gaiman">Neil Gaiman</a> (2002)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Hominids_(novel)" title="Hominids (novel)" class="mw-redirect">Hominids</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_J._Sawyer" title="Robert J. Sawyer">Robert J. Sawyer</a> (2003)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Paladin_of_Souls" title="Paladin of Souls">Paladin of Souls</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Lois_McMaster_Bujold" title="Lois McMaster Bujold">Lois McMaster Bujold</a> (2004)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Jonathan_Strange_%26_Mr_Norrell" title="Jonathan Strange &amp; Mr Norrell">Jonathan Strange &amp; Mr Norrell</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Susanna_Clarke" title="Susanna Clarke">Susanna Clarke</a> (2005)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Spin_(novel)" title="Spin (novel)">Spin</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Robert_Charles_Wilson" title="Robert Charles Wilson">Robert Charles Wilson</a> (2006)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/Rainbows_End" title="Rainbows End">Rainbows End</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Vernor_Vinge" title="Vernor Vinge">Vernor Vinge</a> (2007)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Yiddish_Policemen%27s_Union" title="The Yiddish Policemen's Union">The Yiddish Policemen's Union</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Michael_Chabon" title="Michael Chabon">Michael Chabon</a> (2008)</span></p>
